title: Starts of the Week + Week 9 Breakdown, Time for Launch! - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/4
description:
It’s football time! Week 9 is here and The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, Andy, Mike, and Jason dive into Week 9 matchups and reveal their Starts of the Week! Plus, injury updates, and a new edition of “Never Not Working!” Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 4th, 2021.
  
 (04:00) - Never Not Working
 (13:05) - NFL News
 (26:40) - Fantasy Forecast
 (26:55) - Browns at Bengals
 (31:25) - Broncos at Cowboys
 (37:10) - Texans at Dolphins
 (40:55) - Falcons at Saints
 (47:40) - Raiders at Giants
 (54:20) - Patriots at Panthers
 (57:55) - Starts of the Week
 (58:05) - QB Starts of the Week
 (01:00:15) - RB Starts of the Week
 (01:01:30) - WR Starts of the Week
 (01:04:25) - TE Starts of the Week
 (01:07:25) - Boom Boom Kicker of the Week
